---
import avatar from '../assets/avatar.png';
---

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-950 border-t border-slate-900 reveal">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 text-center">
    
    <span class="font-mono text-primary text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Client Perspectives</span>
    <h2 class="mb-16">Trusted by Canada's Supply Chain Leaders</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-primary/30 transition text-left relative group">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-6xl text-slate-800 font-serif opacity-50 group-hover:text-primary/20 transition">"</div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <img src={avatar.src} alt="Edward B" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover ring-2 ring-primary/50" />
            <div>
                <div class="font-bold text-white">Edward B.</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Director of Procurement, AutoParts Co.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-300 italic relative z-10 leading-relaxed">
          The hybrid model saved us 22% on unit costs last year. But honestly? The real value is the local warehouse. We haven't missed a line-down shipment in 18 months.
        </p>
      </div>

       <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
       <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-primary/30 transition text-left relative group">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-6xl text-slate-800 font-serif opacity-50 group-hover:text-primary/20 transition">"</div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-900/50 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold border border-primary/30">SM</div>
            <div>
                <div class="font-bold text-white">Sarah M.</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Supply Chain Lead, AeroTech</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-300 italic relative z-10 leading-relaxed">
          Finally, a shop that understands 'Risk Management' isn't just a buzzword. The transparency through their digital portal gives my team total peace of mind.
        </p>
      </div>

       <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
       <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-primary/30 transition text-left relative group">
        <div class="absolute top-6 right-8 text-6xl text-slate-800 font-serif opacity-50 group-hover:text-primary/20 transition">"</div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-900/20 flex items-center justify-center text-green-500 font-bold border border-green-500/30">JD</div>
            <div>
                <div class="font-bold text-white">James D.</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">VP Operations, EnergySystems</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-300 italic relative z-10 leading-relaxed">
          We prototype in Mississauga on Tuesday and approve for India production by Friday. The speed of NPI (New Product Introduction) is unmatched.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
